Here are our top 10 picks (Top 10 Barcelona):
CHAPTERS:
0:00 Intro
0:32 #10: Park Gell by Antoni Gaud 
1:24 #9: La Sagrada Famlia by Gaud

4:45 #6: Barceloneta beach, W Hotel, Rambla de Mar, Port of Barcelona, etc.
5:37 #5: Tibidabo 
6:16 #4: Camp Nou football stadium (FC Barcelona)
7:50 #3: Montjuc Castle 
8:26 #2: The Magic Fountain of Montjuc
9:13 #1: Gothic Quarter (Cathedral of Barcelona, Pont del Bisbe, etc.)
10:05 #BONUS
